      <p class="center"><b>THE PROTECTION OF FREEDOMS ACT 2012 (GUIDANCE ON THE MAKING OR RENEWING OF NATIONAL SECURITY DETERMINATIONS) ORDER 2014</b></p>
      <p class="center"><docNumber><b>2014 No. 198</b></docNumber></p>
    </preface>
